      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUCY VALENTINE (1) boasts a strong record this journey here with seven wins and two minors from 15 tries. In the money last time at this track (18.44) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 2.25 lengths second. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. DENAWEN BEACH (6) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (20.23) last time in a Grade 5 at Gunnedah. Form here at the trip sound including seven wins. Can do much better this time. FUSION ROSE (3) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 18.40 beating Hard Style Chick. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Should feature again. TRIPLE PHANTOM (8) generally performs well over this distance.",
